author: Sally Rawsthorne
title: Model petrolhead Kate Peck reveals how she really gets her kicks
text:
SHE’S the model with a love of racing — but it’s on a different sort of track that Kate Peck gets her real kicks.
Peck has had a long love of motorbikes, she reveals.
And this weekend she’s been able to combine her passion with her professional life by covering Phillip Island’s MotoGP for Ten with Daryl Beattie.
“I’ve always loved bikes, and I’ve always loved the MotoGP. To be able to cover it is a dream come true,” she said.
The MTV presenter, who is also a Myer Racing ambassador, is soon to go to the Netherlands to cover more fast bikes for Red Bull TV.
She’s also just shot and co-produced a series called Lid to Lid, in which she interviews celebrities including Matt Moran and Axle Whitehead from the back of a bike.
